# Visual Verification

Start the application, capture screenshots of every key view and state, compare against design references, and present a structured visual report for human approval.

<EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>
You MUST write output to: {{task.changePath}}/visual-report.md

This step verifies and reports. Do NOT fix issues, refactor code, or make changes. If something looks wrong, document it — the implementation step handles fixes.
</EXTREMELY-IMPORTANT>

